quran[16]{c,v,t}:
  50,30,Uroe nyan meukheun ubak nuraka Peue teuma haba ka peunoh di kah Peue na tamah lom jitanyong sigra
  50,31,Soe nyang takwa teuma meutuah Hana that jioh sinan churuga Geutamong lanja keunan le bagah
  50,32,Nyoe nyang geujanji dilee keu gata Sabab dum gata toubat bak Allah Bandum peurintah sabe geujaga
  50,33,Allah Taʻala han tom geubantah Takot keu Tuhan bah hana leumah Han geu tem seumah meunyo kon Allah Toubat lam ate sabe bak Tuhan
  50,34,Keudeh u dalam jak tamong bagah Saleum seulamat keu bandum gata Keukai rok masa sinan geukeubah
  50,35,Peue-peue nyang meuhʻeut di sinan ka nat Nyang laen teuma lom Kamoe tamah
  50,36,Padum le dilee ka peubinasa Nyang teuga-teuga beuho sileupah Leubeh beuho jih nibak awaknyoe Padum le nanggroe ka di jeulajah Ho jikeumeung plueng teuma uroe nyoe
  50,37,Bandum atra nyoe tatueng phaedah Jeut keupeuingat keu soe nyang pike Nyang na lam ate sipheut meutuah Nyang got jideungo peue nyang jikalon
  50,38,Kamoe pakriban kuasa leupah Ka Kamoe peujeut langet ngon bumoe Ngon bandum asoe keubit that bagah Meupeujeut bandum dalam nam uroe Teuma di Kamoe hana meupayah
  50,39,Teuma tasaba jikheun barangpeue Di gata pujoe mantong keu Allah Takheun teuseubeh tapujoe Tuhan Uroe ngon malam sabe di babah Beungoh yoh goh teubiet uroe Goh jilop uroe pih bek takeubah
  50,40,Takheun teuseubeh lom watee malam ‘Oh lheuh seumbahyang sujud bak Allah
  50,41,Beu got tadeungo watee geumeuhoi Le ureueng meuhoi nyang toe sileupah
  50,42,Uroe nyan bandum deungo su raya Su sangka kala cit hana salah Beuna that nyan keuh uroe geunbangket
  50,43,Kamoe peuudep bandum cit mudah Kamoe peuudep Kamoe peumate Meuwoe keudeh le bandum bak Allah Bandum teuh teuma tawoe bak Kamoe
  50,44,Beukah ngon bumoe teubiet dum bagah Meusapat bandum teuma bak Kamoe Teuma atra nyoe leupah that mudah
  50,45,Teuma Kamoe roe nyang leubeh teupue Bah barangkapeue peue nyang jipeugah Hana kreuh gata teuma ateuh jih Tapeuingat jih hana phaedah Deungon Qur'an nyoe tapeuingat Ureueng that takot janji Lon peugah